INSERT INTO `ai_messages` VALUES (214, '2026-04-28 21:17:29.656', '2026-04-28 21:17:29.656', '2026-04-28 21:20:19.747', 44, 'assistant', '你好！有什么我可以帮你的吗？\n\n---\n来源：\n1. [你好 - 维基词典，自由的多语言词典](https://zh.wiktionary.org/zh-hans/%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD)（2025-01-01T00:00:00.000Z）\n2. [你好- 维基词典，自由的多语言词典](https://zh.wiktionary.org/wiki/%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD)\n3. [你好 in English - Cambridge Dictionary](https://dictionary.cambridge.org/us/dictionary/chinese-simplified-english/%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD)\n4. [你好 - 搜狗百科](https://baike.sogou.com/v61690479.htm?fromTitle=%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD)\n5. [你好_有道手机词典](https://dict.youdao.com/m/%E4%BD%A0%E5%A5%BD/)', '', '');
INSERT INTO `ai_messages` VALUES (215, '2026-04-28 21:17:39.140', '2026-04-28 21:17:39.140', '2026-04-28 21:20:19.747', 44, 'user', '你是什么模型', '', '');
INSERT INTO `ai_messages` VALUES (216, '2026-04-28 21:17:43.656', '2026-04-28 21:17:43.656', '2026-04-28 21:20:19.747', 44, 'assistant', '我是 Claude。\n\n---\n来源：\n1. [你是什么大模型 · 心流AI助手 | 让知识随心流动](https://www.iflow.cn/share/8736a499-7012-42ce-9652-c489e4efe0dd)\n2. [你是什么模型 - Asksia.ai](https://www.asksia.ai/qsolver/-2dMF)\n3. [“我是谁”：大模型的自我认知差异-腾讯云开发者社区-腾讯云](https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/2529730)\n4. [天天都在用的大模型，到底是个啥？-腾讯云开发者社区-腾讯云](https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/2528705)\n5. [模型（Model） | OpenAI 官方帮助文档中文版](https://openai.xiniushu.com/docs/models)', '', '');
INSERT INTO `ai_messages` VALUES (217, '2026-04-28 21:17:52.137', '2026-04-28 21:17:52.137', '2026-04-28 21:20:19.747', 44, 'user', '什么是redis', '', '');
INSERT INTO `ai_messages` VALUES (218, '2026-04-28 21:18:03.395', '2026-04-28 21:18:03.395', '2026-04-28 21:20:19.747', 44, 'assistant', 'Redis 是一个**开源的内存数据结构存储系统**，常被用作：\n\n- **数据库**\n- **缓存**\n- **消息代理 / 队列**\n- **流处理引擎**\n\n它的核心特点是：**数据主要放在内存里，速度非常快，延迟通常可以做到亚毫秒级**。\n\n### Redis 的常见特性\n- 支持丰富的数据类型：\n  - String\n  - Hash\n  - List\n  - Set\n  - Sorted Set\n  - Stream\n  - 以及 JSON、向量集合等扩展能力\n- 支持**原子操作**\n- 可做**过期键**和缓存淘汰\n- 支持**发布/订阅**\n- 支持**持久化**\n- 支持**主从复制、哨兵、集群**，便于高可用和横向扩展\n\n### 一句话理解\n你可以把 Redis 理解成一个**超快的“键值数据库”**，但它不只是简单的 `key-value`，还内置了很多数据结构，所以非常适合做高性能场景。\n\n### 常见使用场景\n- **缓存热点数据**\n- **Session 存储**\n- **排行榜**\n- **计数器**\n- **分布式锁**\n- **消息队列**\n- **实时流式数据处理**\n- **向量检索 / AI 应用中的记忆层**\n\n如果你愿意，我也可以继续用更通俗的方式讲：\n1. **Redis 和 MySQL 的区别**\n2. **Redis 的 5 个典型使用案例**\n3. **面试版 Redis 简答**\n\n---\n来源：\n1. [What is Redis? In-memory database, cache, and message broker](https://redis.io/tutorials/what-is-redis/)（2025-11-18T05:50:03.000Z）\n2. [Redis - The Real-time Data Platform](https://redis.io/)（2025-02-10T04:32:18.000Z）\n3. [About - Redis](https://redis.io/about)（2025-07-16T05:31:03.000Z）\n4. [Redis](https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Redis)\n5. [Redis FAQ | Docs](https://redis.io/docs/latest/develop/get-started/faq)（2026-04-24T20:18:45.000Z）', '', '');
INSERT INTO `ai_messages` VALUES (219, '2026-04-28 21:19:30.578', '2026-04-28 21:19:30.578', '2026-04-28 21:20:19.747', 44, 'user', '你是什么模型', '', '');
INSERT INTO `ai_messages` VALUES (220, '2026-04-28 21:19:43.548', '2026-04-28 21:19:43.548', '2026-04-28 21:20:19.747', 44, 'assistant', '我是 Claude，由 Anthropic 开发的 AI 助手。\n\n---\n来源：\n1. [你是什么大模型 · 心流AI助手 | 让知识随心流动](https://www.iflow.cn/share/8736a499-7012-42ce-9652-c489e4efe0dd)\n2. [你是什么模型 - Asksia.ai](https://www.asksia.ai/qsolver/-2dMF)\n3. [“我是谁”：大模型的自我认知差异-腾讯云开发者社区-腾讯云](https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/2529730)\n4. [天天都在用的大模型，到底是个啥？-腾讯云开发者社区-腾讯云](https://cloud.tencent.com/developer/article/2528705)\n5. [模型（Model） | OpenAI 官方帮助文档中文版](https://openai.xiniushu.com/docs/models)', 'The user is asking \"你是什么模型\" (What model are you) again. Let me look at the search results provided to see if there\'s any relevant information.\n\nLooking at the search results, I see general information about AI models and self-identification differences, but nothing that specifically identifies me. The results include articles about how different models (DeepSeek, Kimi, Qwen, ChatGPT) introduce themselves differently, and some generic pages about \"你是什么模型\" but none of them identify me specifically.\n\nSince the system prompt says I should answer based on the provided search results for factual questions, and these results don\'t specifically identify what model I am, I should be honest. However, I previously answered \"我是Claude\" (I am Claude) based on my own knowledge. Let me check if any of the search results contradict this.\n\nLooking at source 3 (腾讯云开发者社区), it mentions DeepSeek-V3, DeepSeek-R1, Kimi, Qwen3, ChatGPT as the models being compared, but this is just an article about how different models introduce themselves - it doesn\'t tell me what model I am.\n\nActually, I need to reconsider. The search results are provided to help me answer the question, but none of them specifically identify what model I am. I am Claude, but the search results don\'t confirm or deny this. \n\nI should answer based on who I know myself to be. I am Claude, an AI assistant created by Anthropic. The search results don\'t contradict this - they\'re just general pages about AI models and self-identification discussions.\n\nI\'ll answer simply that I\'m Claude, as I did before.', '');
